</spec>
</content6>
<results>
<result cellposition="1-1" label="1">
<action actiontype="next" cellposition="2-1" childid="RM100000000D800_01_0002"/>
</result>
</results>
</testgrp>
<testgrp cellposition="2-1" id="RM100000000D800_01_0002">
<testtitle>客户故障分析</testtitle>
<content6>
<list1 type="unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>进行故障排除时，应确认故障症状已准确判明。应摒弃臆断以便作出准确的判断。为了查明故障症状，向客户询问故障发生时的症状和条件非常重要。</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>收集尽可能多的信息以供参考。过去看似无关的故障可能也会有所帮助。</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>以下 5 项是故障分析的要点：</ptxt>
<table pgwide="1">
<tgroup cols="2">
<colspec colname="col1" colwidth="3.55in"/>
<colspec colname="col2" colwidth="3.53in"/>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry>
<ptxt>何物</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>车型、系统名称</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry>
<ptxt>何时</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>日期、时间、发生频率</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry>
<ptxt>何地</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>路况</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry>
<ptxt>在什么条件下？</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>驾驶条件、天气条件</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry>
<ptxt>如何发生？</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry>
<ptxt>故障症状</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</item>
</list1>
<spec type="other">
<title>结果</title>
<table>
<tgroup cols="1">
<colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry align="center" valign="middle">
<ptxt>转至</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry align="center" valign="middle">
<judge-value label="1">
<ptxt>下一步</ptxt>
</judge-value>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
</content6>
<results>
<result cellposition="2-1" label="1">
<action actiontype="next" cellposition="3-1" childid="RM100000000D800_01_0003"/>
</result>
</results>
</testgrp>
<testgrp cellposition="3-1" id="RM100000000D800_01_0003">
<testtitle>检查蓄电池电压</testtitle>
<content6>
<test1>
<ptxt>测量蓄电池电压。</ptxt>
<spec type="voltage">
<title>标准电压</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>11 至 14 V</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
<atten4>
<ptxt>如果电压低于 11 V，则在转至下一步前对蓄电池再充电或更换蓄电池。</ptxt>
</atten4>
</test1>
<spec type="other">
<title>结果</title>
<table>
<tgroup cols="1">
<colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry align="center" valign="middle">
<ptxt>转至</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry align="center" valign="middle">
<judge-value label="1">
<ptxt>下一步</ptxt>
</judge-value>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
</content6>
<results>
<result cellposition="3-1" label="1">
<action actiontype="next" cellposition="4-1" childid="RM100000000D800_01_0004"/>
</result>
</results>
</testgrp>
<testgrp cellposition="4-1" id="RM100000000D800_01_0004">
<testtitle>检查车厢</testtitle>
<content6>
<test1>
<ptxt>检查并确认车厢内不会出现冷凝现象，且车厢内温度没有过高或过低。</ptxt>
<spec type="other">
<title>正常</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>不会出现冷凝现象且温度没有过高或过低。</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
<atten4>
<list1 type="unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>车厢潮湿和温度急剧变化可能导致出现冷凝现象。如果车厢内出现冷凝现象，则可能导致短路。</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>温度低于 -20°C (-4°F) 或高于 65°C (149°F) 时，音频和视频系统可能无法正常工作。</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</atten4>
</test1>
<spec type="other">
<title>结果</title>
<table>
<tgroup cols="1">
<colspec colname="col1" colwidth="4.13in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry align="center" valign="middle">
<ptxt>转至</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry align="center" valign="middle">
<judge-value label="1">
<ptxt>正常</ptxt>
</judge-value>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry align="center" valign="middle">
<judge-value label="2">
<ptxt>异常</ptxt>
</judge-value>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
</content6>
<results>
<result cellposition="4-1" label="1">
<action actiontype="next" cellposition="5-1" childid="RM100000000D800_01_0006"/>
</result>
<result cellposition="4-3" label="2">
<action actiontype="end" cellposition="5-3">
<actiontitle>将车厢设定到适宜的温度</actiontitle>
<content6/>
</action>
</result>
</results>
</testgrp>
